{"word":"λευστήρ","slug":"λευστήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n62786\" key=\"leusth/r\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λευστήρ</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ῆρος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">λεύω</etym>) <sense id=\"n62786.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">one who stones</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg011.perseus-grc1:1039\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1039</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸν Κασσανδρέων λευστῆρα</foreign> their <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">oppressor</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg001:5:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ NA\">NA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.15</biblScope> </bibl>; so perh. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:67\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.67</biblScope></bibl>, where the oracle tells Cleisthenes <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἄδρηστον μὲν εἶναι Σικυωνίων βασιλέα, ἐκεῖνον δὲ λευστῆρα</foreign> (or perh. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a mere stone-thrower</tr_>, i.e. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψιλός</foreign>: <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author></bibl>, quoting <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg004:115\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">115</biblScope></bibl>, makes it <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ὁ καταλευσθῆναι ἄξιος</ref> </xr>). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n62786.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adj.\">Adj.</a></pos>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λ. μόρος</foreign> death <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">by stoning</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg004.perseus-grc1:199\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">199</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">λευστῆρα πρῶτον . . ῥίψας πέτρον</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lyc.\">Lyc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1187</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}